&lt;p&gt;&lt;!-- x-tinymce/html --&gt;Study the given table and answer the question that follows.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The table shows loan disbursed (in Rs. crores) by four banks in different years.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;table border=&quot;1&quot; cellpadding=&quot;1&quot; cellspacing=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;width: 330px;&quot;&gt;
